an><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">and it will cause us all difficulty and affect the efficiency and economy </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">for</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> us all.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">This much more </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">important than a tweak of Part P,</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:8pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">We certainly intend to </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">continue to </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">play our part in </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">designing new qualifications and </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">encouraging people to do the right thing.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:8pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Submitted for your consideration. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a href="http://www.tradeskills4u.co.uk" target="_blank"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">www.tradeskills4u.co.uk</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> </span><br /><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:8pt 0pt 0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">3 December 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">1</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>